page.title: 03Housing in W.Norfolk cont.
page.content: In North Lynn housing is intensive.There is a large council house estate.Some of the houses are now privately owned. A three bedroomed semi-detached house could be purchased from around{Â£18,000.}The majority of this property is rented. The rents vary from around{Â£10 to Â£18.50}per week,depending on whether it is a flat,maisonette or semi-detached house. Most property in our area is less than thirty years old and the majority of the developments on the Grange estate and in South Wootton have taken place in the last twenty years.
